---
// Reusable hero backdrop across the site: vivid colour mesh + rotating
// sheen + cursor parallax (motion.js drives --px/--py on the [data-parallax]
// wrapper). Continuous, CSS-only, covers the whole section, frozen under
// prefers-reduced-motion. Drop inside a `position: relative; overflow:
// hidden` hero wrapper.
---
<div class="aurora" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="aurora-field" data-parallax>
    <span class="aurora-blob aurora-1"></span>
    <span class="aurora-blob aurora-2"></span>
    <span class="aurora-blob aurora-3"></span>
    <span class="aurora-sheen"></span>
  </div>
</div>
